<title>USA: IVAX gets approval for bladder disease drug.</title>
<headline>IVAX gets approval for bladder disease drug.</headline>
<dateline>MIAMI 1996-09-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>IVAX said on Monday it has received U.S. Food and Drug Administration approval for its Elmiron drug to treat bladder pain or discomfort from interstitial cystitis.</p>
<p>The disease has similar symptons of a bladder infection, but it cannot be diagnosed by urinalysis and symptoms do not respond to antibiotics, IVAX said.</p>
